<h2>Follow these instructions for a successful weekend care experience:</h2>
<ol>
<h4>
<li>Remove all dishes from <em>EVERY</em> cage - soak in bleach and dish soap minimum 10 minutes.</li>
<li>Provide fresh water to <em>EVERY</em> cage. Do not reuse old water dishes.</li>
<li>Mealworms should already be weighed out. Separate mealworms from media by sifting media into trash</em></li>
<li>Feed cages as directed for each room:

</h4>

<ol type="a">
<li><h3>Colony Room</h3>
<% if @colony_cages.length == 0 %>
No Colony cages to feed.
<% else %>
<% for cage in @colony_cages %>
<table>
<th>Name</th>
<th>Food</th>
<th>Dishes</th>
<tr>
  <td><%= cage.name %></td>
  <td><%= cage.food %>g</td>
  <td><%=h cage.dish_num %> <%=h cage.dish_type %></td>
<tr>
</table>
<% end %>
<% end %>
</li>

<li>
<h3>Belfry</h3>
<% if @belfry_cages.length == 0 %>
No Belfry cages to feed.
<% else %>
<% for cage in @belfry_cages %>
